# ORIG TITLE    KFC revamps its reputation in China . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Wooing the Chinese. KFC has launched a campaign to rebuild its brand in China following a scandal over banned drugs being used to fatten chickens in its supply chain. The company has promised a zero tolerance approach to food safety abuses. The largest fast-food chain in China has seen a 37 per cent slump in sales since the scandal hit. 
